48:42.796 --> 48:45.378
And even though most of you hate me...

48:45.548 --> 48:47.539
...I love just about everybody here.

48:47.717 --> 48:49.093
I know what you think of me...

48:49.260 --> 48:51.751
...that some of you blame me
for what's happened.

48:52.764 --> 48:54.800
And you're not wrong.

48:55.892 --> 48:57.302
I played a part.

48:57.477 --> 49:00.059
But we can't go back
to the way things were.

49:00.814 --> 49:04.147
And I can't save those
who have been lost.

49:05.443 --> 49:08.185
But some of our loved ones
are fighting for their lives...

49:08.363 --> 49:10.945
...and for better or for worse,
nobody in this town...

49:11.116 --> 49:13.653
...knows vampires better than me.

49:16.704 --> 49:18.490
I wanna help.

49:20.792 --> 49:23.078
Please, let me help.
